Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:32.24,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I'm calling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:37.85,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I'm on my way to find the eternal verities
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.03,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Exploding all the teardrops by the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:48.88,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I can feel my heart beating
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:58.87,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}I can see my fate all spinning around beyond the time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:02.32,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Rise up to the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:04.96,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Like a butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.58,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Show me what's inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:10.23,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Don't ever let go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:15.68,JOJO4-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur15}Shining stars will guide me to somewhere high
